import React, { Component } from 'react'
import { Menu, Icon } from 'antd'

export default class Nav extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <Menu onClick={this.handleClick} mode="horizontal">
        <Menu.Item key="UsHomeer">
          <Icon type="home" />
          Home
          </Menu.Item>
        <Menu.Item key="User">
          <Icon type="user" />
          User
          </Menu.Item>
        <Menu.Item key="Logout">
          <Icon type="logout" />
          Logout
        </Menu.Item>
      </Menu>
    )
  }
}
